---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="yaopulife DIY Privacy Policy - How we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <Navbar />
  
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500">Last updated: May 13, 2026</p>
      
      <div class="mt-12 prose prose-lg text-gray-600">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us when you:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fill out our contact or custom order forms</li>
          <li>Subscribe to our email newsletter</li>
          <li>Chat with us via Tidio or WhatsApp</li>
          <li>Upload reference images for custom orders</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This may include your name, email address, custom requirements, and uploaded images.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your inquiries and process custom orders</li>
          <li>To send AI design previews and order updates</li>
          <li>To send marketing emails (only if you subscribe)</li>
          <li>To improve our website and services</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">3. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>Your data is stored securely with our service providers (Sanity CMS, Resend, Klaviyo). We retain order information for 2 years for customer service purposes.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">4. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. Contact us at hello@yaopulife.com for any privacy-related requests.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use essential cookies for website functionality and analytics cookies (with your consent) to understand how visitors use our site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
